	Pole perfect    
	 Los Angeles, March 10 (PTI): Demi Moore gave daughter Rumer Willis a pole-dancing lesson during a recent party at Hollywoods celeb hot-spot Chateau Marmont.       
	The Ghost actress and 21-year-old Rumer Willis attended a recent party at the Chateau Marmont and the 47-year-old actress was keen to show off her raunchy moves, reports Life and Style magazine.      
	 Demi got up and impressed everyone, especially when she spun around the pole upside down, said an onlooker. Rumer, the actresss eldest daughter from her marriage to actor Bruce Willis, then decided to follow in her mothers footsteps by giving it a go.    
